Interface RateIndexSecurity

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Security
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IborFutureSecurity, OvernightFutureSecurity

    public interface RateIndexSecurity
extends Security
    An instrument representing a security associated with a rate index.

    Examples include Ibor or Overnight rate futures.
